snippet.title: ➿ Meaningless Trailer - Wishlist Now ✨
snippet.description:
Solve puzzles by moving blocks to guide the ball to the exit in a minimalist 3D world. Take the time to appreciate your success, it's hypnotic and satisfying to watch.

Buy on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2412190/Meaningless/
Buy on Itch.io: https://duck-reaction.itch.io/meaningless
Buy on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.duckreaction.anoddlysatisfyinggame
